[gd_resource type="Resource" script_class="HandbookPage" load_steps=2 format=3]

[ext_resource type="Script" path="res://resources/HandbookPage.gd" id="1_page"]

[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_page")
page_id = "email"
title = "EMAIL FORENSIC PROTOCOL"
content = "[b][color=#006CFF]INVESTIGATIVE CHECKLIST[/color][/b]
Email is the #1 threat vector. Follow this checklist for every suspected phishing alert:

1. [b]Verify Headers[/b]: Check if the sender's address matches the display name. Look for SPF failures.
2. [b]Scan Attachments[/b]: Never download a file without running it through the sandbox scan.
3. [b]Check Links[/b]: Scan domains for reputation. If a domain is pulsing Cyan, it is already blacklisted.

[b][color=#C62828]PRO TIP:[/color][/b] After you find a malicious IP or Domain in an email, you must go to the SIEM to see if anyone clicked it."
